---
title: Scandi-Style Salmon with Pickled Shallot Dressing
description: Summer flavours, made cozy! Dilly buttered potatoes are paired with honey and mustard glazed salmon. Marinated shallots double-up as a dressing and salad topper for a puckery pickled pop!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/scandi-style-salmon-740f69b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/scandi-style-salmon-61921e5a12f5a569406937a8-b9241789.pdf
